            <h1>DuBois man creates app to help friends hang out</h1>
            <div class="synopsis" tag=""> 
              A DuBois man has now created an app that he said will help friends coordinate free time with each other. “We had a bunch of friends on Facebook but we didn’t know if any of them were free or any of them were on campus,” said Adam Elkassas. So he and a group of friends made a free mobile app he said will help you avoid the guessing game when it comes to trying to find someone to hang out with. It’s called Down to Chill.
